    Join community
  </p> -->
  <p class="text-center py-1 mx-auto bg-gray-200 text-gray-600 w-3/4 rounded-full font-sans font-medium text-xs hover:bg-gray-300"><%= link_to "Join community", join_community_path(community), method: :post, class:"block" %></p>
</div>

